msgstr "fotografija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module allows you to configure support for your digital camera."
msgstr "Ta modul omogoča konfiguracijo podpore za vašo digitalno kamero."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Add</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to select the camera's model and the port it is connected "
"to on your computer (&eg; USB, Serial). If your camera does not appear in "
"the list of <guilabel>Supported Cameras</guilabel>, go to the <ulink url="
"\"http://www.gphoto.org\">GPhoto web site</ulink> for a possible update."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, da izberete model kamere in vrata, s katerimi je povezana "
"v računalniku (&eg; USB, Serial). Če vašega fotoaparata ni na seznamu "
"<guilabel>Podprte kamere</guilabel>, obiščite <ulink url=\"http://www.gphoto."
"org\">Strani GPhoto</ulink> za morebitno posodobitev."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Test"
msgstr "Test"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click this button to test the connection to the selected camera."
msgstr "S klikom na ta gumb preizkusite povezavo z izbrano kamero."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove"
msgstr "Odstrani"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the selected camera from the list."
msgstr "Odstranit izbrano kamero s seznama."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to change the configuration of the selected camera. The "
"availability of this feature and the contents of the Configuration dialog "
"depend on the camera model."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ta gumb, če želite spremeniti konfiguracijo izbrane kamere. "
"Razpoložljivost te funkcije in vsebina pogovornega okna za konfiguracijo sta "
"odvisni od modela kamere."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Information"
msgstr "Informacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click this button to view a summary of the current status of the selected "
"camera. The availability of this feature and the contents of the Information "
"dialog depend on the camera model."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na ta gumb si lahko ogledate povzetek trenutnega stanja izbrane "
"kamere. Razpoložljivost te funkcije in vsebina pogovornega okna Informacije "
"sta odvisni od modela kamere."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "Prekliči"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click this button to cancel the current camera operation."
msgstr "Kliknite ta gumb, če želite preklicati trenutno delovanje fotoaparata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and download images from the digital camera, enter "
"<userinput>camera:/</userinput> in &konqueror;&apos;s or &dolphin;&apos;s "
"location bar."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati in prenesti slike iz digitalnega fotoaparata, vnesite "
"<userinput>camera:/</userinput> v &konqueror;&apos;s ali &dolphin;&apos;s "
"lokacijsko vrstico."
